83","type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":"良問","ts":"1531624214.000041","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"5946ab82-2139-4f44-b0e2-016287a076d5","type":"message","user":"UBRTB4N5C","text":"トグルだと operation との組み合わせのときに連打の方が使えないという問題はありそう。","ts":"1531625889.000003","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"65d04521-8eab-4fba-a2f1-ce654d3b4f99","type":"message","user":"U7ZUUQSBT","text":"例えばなのですが、`:global /\\v^x\\s/ d`  するときに、下記の例で行くと `cursor positon` が `row 4 -&gt; row 5` なのですが `row 4 -&gt; row 3` にすることは可能でしょうか？ヒントいただけると嬉しいです (^_^)/\n\n```\n --------------------------------------------------------\n        global コマンド実行時のカーソル位置の挙動\n --------------------------------------------------------\n\n// 現在のすがた\n1: x  foo                  1: xx foo\n2: xx foo                  2:\n3:                         3:\n4: |        ---------&gt;     4:\n5:                         5: |xx foo\n6: x  foo                  6:\n7: xx foo                  7:\n\n\n// ほしい挙動\n1: x  foo                  1: xx foo\n2: xx foo                  2:\n3:                         3: |\n4: |        ---------&gt;     4:\n5:                         5: xx foo\n6: x  foo                  6:\n7: xx foo                  7:\n```","ts":"1531634695.000021","edited":{"user":"U7ZUUQSBT","ts":"1531635467.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"}]
